        Gets the value of the 'specs' field. Must be one or more IRIs identifying resources for installing or enabling the software. Implementations may provide resolvers which map well-known software spec IRIs to some configuration action. An IRI `https://anaconda.org/bioconda/bowtie` could be resolved with `conda install -c bioconda bowtie`.
